<dl id="n40072d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40072d">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40072d"> 72(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ethereal / ariel ) body </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Augustine also says (Gen. ad lit. iii): &ldquo;The demons are called animals of the atmosphere because their nature is akin to that of aerial bodies.&rdquo; But the nature of demons and angels is the same. Therefore angels have bodies naturally united to them. </mm> </dd></dl>
